             were indicted for <rs id="t18091101-57-off335" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18091101-57-off335" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18091101-57-off335" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18091101-57-cd336" type="crimeDate">9th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18091101-57-off335 t18091101-57-cd336"></join>, a seven shilling piece, half a crown, five shillings, and a sixpence, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18091101-57-victim493" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Bromley
                        <interp inst="t18091101-57-victim493" type="surname" value="Bromley"></interp>
